# The [[time]] of [[noon]]; the time of [[day]] when the [[sun]] is [[highest]] in the sky, especially on a [[hot]] day.

====Synonyms====
*{{italbrac|time of noon}}: [[midday]], [[noon]]

====Quotations====
*'''1858''' — [[w:Henry Wadsworth Longfellow|Henry Wadsworth Longfellow]], ''[[s:The Courtship of Miles Standish|The Courtship of Miles Standish]]'', part 9
*:She should not walk, he said, through the dust and heat of the '''noonday''';<br/>Nay, she should ride like a queen, not plod along like a peasant.

